result.execSummary:
The defendant was charged with both OWI (3rd w/ Passenger < 16 Yrs Old) [Modifiers: Penalty - Operating While under the Influence (3rd Offense)] and Operating w/PAC-Passenger < 16 Yrs (3rd) [Modifiers: Penalty - Operating While under the Influence (3rd Offense)]. The defendant was found guilty of OWI (3rd w/ Passenger < 16 Yrs Old) [Modifiers: Penalty - Operating While under the Influence (3rd Offense)] and the other charge, Operating w/PAC-Passenger < 16 Yrs (3rd) [Modifiers: Penalty - Operating While under the Influence (3rd Offense)] was dismissed by the court.

  • Rebecca L. Gladem was found guilty of OWI (3rd w/ Passenger < 16 Yrs Old) [Modifiers: Penalty - Operating While under the Influence (3rd Offense)], an unclassified felony, Wisconsin Statutes 346.63(1)(a).
